Summary: Descend and and shoot into the sky....
divs: Sighting DetailsMy father called to tell me that my brother had seen 6 triangle ufos with his daughters when he arrived at my fathers house in South Hadley and when he went outside to see this he noticed five vehicles descend do a check mark in the sky and shoot up into the sky.
trends: There have been no other sightings in South Hadley
This sighting has never been favorited.
